<doc f='tvm/include/tvm/tir/expr.h' l='656'>/*! \brief Set the dtype based on the buffer/indices
   *
   * Usually, the BufferLoad&apos;s dtype will be the same dtype as the
   * buffer.  This may have a different number of lanes than the
   * buffer&apos;s dtype if index values have more than 1 lane.
   *
   * This function should only be called during construction and after
   * CopyOnWrite.  Friend class used here to restrict usage.
   */</doc>
